caption:
4.4.3 Results. Experimental results on NUS-81-Web are shown in 
Table 3. Our proposed method outperforms baseline model and 
the model finetuned by only CNN labels for all three metrics. For 
the mAP score, we achieve 0.9% improvement using VSGraph-LC 
compared to the pretrained model. Our method can also increase 
both C-F1 and O-F1 by 1.1% and 0.6%, respectively. Unlike the 
performance on WebVision, finetuning with CNN labels brings no 
significant improvement on C-F1 and mAP, and even a 0.4% drop 
on O-F1. This demonstrates that under a high noisy-level setting 
like NUS-81-Web, labels corrected by our VSGraph-LC method are 
more reliable than the CNN labels.
